&lt;h2&gt;Campaigning at Teneo&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Campaigning is the way we think about corporate communications. We define it as creating high impact moments over time, and at scale, that cause audiences to pause and think about an organisation. It’s communicating in an organised and active way, towards a goal.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our approach is to consider all audiences. In a climate that no longer respects boundaries or disciplines, we are not limited by sector divisions or traditional silos like ‘consumer’, ‘corporate’ or ‘digital’. We organise our skills and expertise under one campaigning approach – drawing on disciplines including social, digital, traditional media relations, content creation, employee engagement, issues management – to reach the audiences that matter. We bring together sophisticated researchers, brilliant creatives, well-connected media operators, expert brand and social strategists, financial market specialists, geopolitical intelligence, organisational change specialists, as well as seasoned political and social campaigners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Working at Teneo&lt;/h2&gt;
