&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity for an experienced Forensic Technology Director to join Teneo, the global CEO advisory firm, within our Financial Advisory business, based in the Cayman Islands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team work with clients across the Caribbean and internationally on complex litigation, arbitration, investigations, regulatory matters and disputes. We pride ourselves on delivering exceptional client services, in line with industry standards and specific individual needs of our clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The specific role will be dependent upon the experience of the candidate. The overall role will be to support the delivery of client engagements for our Forensic Technology service line, covering all areas of the EDRM lifecycle. You will be part of a growing, experienced team with room for professional growth.&lt;/p&gt;
