&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of experience delivering forensic technology, digital forensics or eDiscovery engagements within a professional services, consulting or legal services environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Client facing Project Management experience in industry is essential. Strong client management and communication skills, including the ability to communicate complex ideas and data management approaches effectively to a non-technical audience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive experience administering and delivering large-scale eDiscovery matters using Relativity. Relativity Certified Administrator (RCA) is essential. Additional Relativity certifications are advantageous.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience conducting forensic collections and investigations would be advantageous.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ambitious and motivated, with strong task management skills, alongside ability to solve problems and work to deadlines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Degree or formal cert

