&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Our Management Consulting division advises senior leaders on strategic issues that define the success of their organisations. We combine rigorous analysis, commercial judgement and deep sector&amp;nbsp;expertise&amp;nbsp;with the broader capabilities of Teneo to help clients solve complex business challenges and deliver meaningful outcomes.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
